The problem here is inflation.  I do not mean inflation in the monetary sense; I´m talking about equipment inflation.

When Everquest was released low, mid, and high level jewelry was sought after as it was very good equipment for the time.  Unfortunately, with the expansions drops have become better and better while jewelry has remained basically the same.  

In my opinion, equipment that was great at the design of the game should be great five years later.  This, however, is not the most profitable situation from the designer´s point of view.  They would like to see us all continue playing for that next best item.

